      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/kenya-ditches-dream-for-balanced-budget-as-revenue-lags-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚将不得不继续借贷以资助其预算，倾销计划将其支出与2027年的收入相匹配。]]></description>
