    <item>
      <title>华尔街奖励池攀登以记录为利润飞涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-26/wall-street-bonus-pool-climbs-to-record-as-profits-soar-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着行业利润飙升，华尔街奖金的总奖金飙升至创纪录的475亿美元。年平均奖金增长了几乎三分之一，达到244,700美元，这是自19号大流行以来的首次显着增长。詹妮弗·苏兰（Jennifer Surane）在彭博电视台上报告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-26/wall-street-bonus-pool-climbs-to-record-as-profits-soar-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 10:32:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
